title: Apple CEO Tim Cook to Deliver Virtual Commencement Address for Ohio State University Students
description: Apple CEO Tim Cook will deliver the commencement address at Ohio State University's virtual commencement event that's set to take place on May 3, Ohio State President Michael Drake announced today. The event, which will be live streamed, will kick off at noon…
